<div class="status-form-container">
    <div class="form-header">
        <h1 class="form-title">Nh·∫≠p Downtime</h1>
        <div class="form-sub">Ch·ªçn Operation trong ng√†y, tr·∫°ng th√°i v√† m√¥ t·∫£ (t√πy ch·ªçn)</div>
